<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome Back</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #89f7fe, #66a6ff);
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #66a6ff;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #66a6ff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #89b6ff;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome Back, <%= name %>!</h1>
        <p>
            We're thrilled to have you back with us. Take a moment to explore the latest insights and updates 
            from our project. Your engagement helps us make a difference!
        </p>
        <a href="/insights" class="btn">View Insights</a>
        <footer>
            Regards, <br/>
            Kamal Sharma <br/>
            MSc in High Integrity Systems, Frankfurt University of Applied Sciences
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
